    "excerpt": "\"Night Prayer (for Older Children) by Rabbi Clifton Harby Levy is found in <em><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=50110\">The Helpful Manual</a></em> (Centre of Jewish Science, 1927), p. 27.  . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contribute a translation</a></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Source (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nI thank You, dear God,<br />\nfor all the fine day of play and lessons.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nI thank You, too,<br />\nfor all the love that has come to me<br />\nfrom my parents,<br />\nmy brothers and sisters<br />\nand friends.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nLet me sleep in peace,<br />\nso that when I wake<br />\nI shall be ready<br />\nfor all I want to do,<br />\nall I want to learn.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nBless all whom I love<br />\nand who love me,<br />\nwith health and happiness.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>&#8220;Night Prayer (for Older Children) by Rabbi Clifton Harby Levy is found in <em><a href=\"/?p=50110\">The Helpful Manual</a></em> (Centre of Jewish Science, 1927), p. 27. </p>\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<style